了服务性能下降。\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU usage significantly increased, affecting service response times (rrt_max)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage changed from 0.01 to 0.6; rrt_max increased from 43028.0 to 178438.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increase in service latency (rrt_max), indicating potential resource contention\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max changed from 3110.0 to 8343.0 during the fault.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n``` \n\n这些异常可能是由于 CPU 使用量和进程数显著增加导致容器性能下降，从而影响了服务响应时间。继续收集更多数据（如日志或跟踪）可能进一步帮助明确根因。", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据收集到的调用链追踪数据，以下是初步发现的显著异常调用链。\n\n### 异常分析\n从数据中分析发现以下特征：\n- 延迟指标显著异常：某些服务的 `anomaly_avg_duration` 是正常时段的 5 倍以上。\n- 异常集中某些核心服务上：`AdService` (广告服务) 和 `CartService` (购物车服务) 延迟较为突出。\n- 下游错误传播路径可能存在：具体由调用树分析得出更明确的根因。\n\n### JSON 格式的初步分析\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->AdService\",\n    \"checkoutservice->ShippingService\",\n    \"checkoutservice->CartService\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"AdService\",\n      \"reason\": \"响应时间大幅上升，异常平均耗时远高于正常值。\",\n      \"evidence\": {\n        \"normal_duration\": 5549.49,\n        \"anomaly_duration\": 50411.64,\n        \"multiplier\": 9.09\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"购物车服务涉及的多个调用均出现了明显延迟，从 Redis 到 Checkout 的整个交互均显示异常。\",\n      \"evidence\": {\n        \"trace_points\": [\n          \"Redis HGET\",\n          \"CartService EmptyCart\",\n          \"Frontend -> CartService\"\n        ],\n        \"multiplier_ranges\": [4.9, 6.3]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ShippingService\",\n      \"reason\": \"调用 ShippingService 的请求处理较平常慢，但波动范围较小。\",\n      \"evidence\": {\n        \"normal_duration\": 185.06,\n        \"anomaly_duration\": 760.5,\n        \"multiplier\": 4.1\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n#### 下一步计划\n- 深入分析每个异常的根因。\n- 查找更多错误日志、异常模式并结合依赖图确认根因服务是否下游传播。\n- 验证是否存在快速失败 (fast fail) 等网络特性问题。"}
